This is Perl module Plack::Middleware::HTMLLint.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - Plack::Middleware::HTMLLint

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
Plack::Middleware::HTMLLint:

    $ cpanm Plack::Middleware::HTMLLint

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf Plack-Middleware-HTMLLint-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd Plack-Middleware-HTMLLint-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Plack::Middleware::HTMLLint documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Plack::Middleware::HTMLLint

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

